
### Buscar todos os pedidos
GET http://localhost:40000/pedidos HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### Buscar pedido por ID
POST http://localhost:40000/pedidos/id HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "pedidoid": 1
}


### Inserir pedido
POST http://localhost:40000/pedidos HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "clienteid": 1,
    "valor": 100.0,
    "data": "2025-09-16"
}


### Atualizar pedido
PUT http://localhost:40000/pedidos HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "clienteid": 1,
    "valor": 170.0,
    "data": "2025-09-17"
}


### Excluir pedido
DELETE http://localhost:40000/pedidos HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "pedidoid": 1
}